replies.msg:
Leon Goretzka on not being in the starting line-up yesterday: &quot;I'm currently in top form, probably the best in my entire career. Of course I'm not happy when I don't play from the start .You can say that openly and honestly. But it's the decision of the coach that has to be accepted.&quot;<br />
<br />
Salihamidžić on Goretzka's statement: &quot;I know what he means, and I also know that he is always upset when he's not playing. Therefore, when he comes in, he should give his best, then the coach will start him again. I prefer we discuss these topics internally.&quot;

